                <h4>What is the voting age population of Ralls, Texas?</h4>
                <p>
                    The total voting age population of Ralls, Texas, meaning US citizens 18 or older, is 1,307.  The voting age population is 42.5% male and 57.5% female.
                </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Ralls, Texas residents are senior citizens?</h4>
                    <p>
                        According to the latest census statistics, 18.6% of
                        the residents of Ralls are 65 or older.
                    </p>
                

                
                    

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    
                    
                    <h4>What are the racial demographics of Ralls, Texas?</h4>
                    <p>The racial demographics of Ralls are 88.8% White, 7.5% Other, 2.6% Black and 1.0% Asian. Additionally, 63.5% of the population identifies as Hispanic.</p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Ralls, Texas residents are below the poverty line?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Ralls, 12.4% of
                    residents have an income below the poverty line, and the child poverty rate
                    is 15.3%.
                    On a per-household basis,
                    11.1% of families are below
                    the poverty line in Ralls.
                    </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Ralls, Texas residents are in the labor force?</h4>
                    <p>
                    Among those aged 16 and older, 57.3% of
                    Ralls residents are in the labor force.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                <h4>What are the education levels among Ralls, Texas residents?</h4>
                <p>Among the adult population 25 years old and over,
                    72.6% of
                    Ralls residents have at least a high school degree or
                    equivalent, 10.8%
                    have a bachelor's degree and 3.9%
                    have a graduate or professional degree.
                

                
                
                <h4>What percentage of Ralls, Texas residents speak a non-English language at home?</h4>
                <p>
                Among Ralls residents aged 5 and older, 40.2% of them speak a non-English language at home.
                Broken down by language:
                39.1% of residents speak Spanish at home,
                0.0% speak an Indo-European language, and
                1.1% speak an Asian language.

                </p>
                

                
    


                
                
                    <h4>What is the unemployment rate in Ralls, Texas?</h4>
                    <p>
                        The unemployment rate in Ralls is 6.2%, which is calculated among residents aged 16 or older who are in the labor force.
                    </p>

                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Ralls, Texas residents work for the government?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Ralls, 16.0% of the
                    residents in the non-military labor force 
                    are employed by the local, state and federal government.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
